  "title": "Team Leader (Warehouse Operations) #78926",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Logistics/ Manufacturing & Production</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Team Leader (Warehouse Operations)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Jurong Island (Company transportation provided)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 8.00am – 5.45pm); Ad hoc Night Shift (8.00pm – 8.00am) (Only when needed)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $2,200 + Allowances + OT + Incentive + AWS + PB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Assign tasks to team members based on priorities and deadlines.</li><li>Work with shift teams to plan container deliveries and delegate tasks to operations assistants.</li><li>Inform the Assistant Supervisor/Supervisor promptly about container delays or operational issues.</li><li>Coordinate and collaborate within the team and with other departments.</li><li>Support onboarding and training of new team members on warehouse processes and safety.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Strong knowledge of warehouse safety and ability to apply best practices across the team.</li><li>Valid forklift licence.</li><li>Basic computer literacy.</li><li>Able to work independently and lead a team effectively.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78926 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
